{
  "stem": "11611.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She lived in La Jolla.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, she had an apartment there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I would see her on weekends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had no options.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did it myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they were presented with a bunch of facts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't consult them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bear in mind, all of this was done when I was living in-- my family was in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in Boston or Cambridge, Massachusetts, going to law school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was nothing to talk about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have any reaction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they kind of expected I would do something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew I-- they knew I had peculiarities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was much too young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was maybe 10 years old at this time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The service wasn't desperate enough to look at him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Til 1946.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a divorce.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was with the 4th Marine Division from its inception until it was disbanded in 19-- the end of '45 or '46.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went wherever the division went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first thing we did was around the end of '43-- get on board ship to go Kwajalein Atoll, where we were scheduled to take a couple of Japanese-held islands, which we did.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I was assigned some duty function on New Year's Eve 1943, '44, which was kind of grim because we were getting aboard ship the next day or two.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then somewhere along the line, I had a couple days off, so I went up to Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, nobody in my family lived in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just a-- an unknown city, for all practical purposes. remember talking to the French mistress of ceremonies at some bar or a hotel who assured me-- and I liked this very well-- that I would survive the war.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
